<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Climate Solutions</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@3.7.1/dist/full.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-base-200 text-base-content">


  <div class="navbar bg-base-100 shadow-md mb-6">
    <div class="flex-1">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost text-xl"> Climate Solutions</a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-none">
      <ul class="menu menu-horizontal px-1">
        <li><a href="about.ejs">About</a></li>
        <li>
          <details>
            <summary>Sector</summary>
            <ul class="p-2 bg-base-100">
              <li>Energy</li>
              <li>Transportation</li>
              <li>Agriculture</li>
            </ul>
          </details>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
 
    <div class="hero bg-base-100 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="max-w-md">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Explore Projects</h1>
          <p class="py-6 text-lg">Get ideas about impactfull climate change solution across variety of different areas.</p>
          <a href="project.ejs" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Projects</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- First Project  -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
        <figure><img src="clime.webp" alt="Climeworks" class="rounded-t-lg" /></figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Climeworks - Direct Air Capture</h2>
          <p>Makes use of modular machines to pull CO2 from air and permanently stores it underground. The company began its operations in Iceland. </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="climeworks.ejs" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Second Project  -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
        <figure><img src="greenwall.jpg" alt="Great Green Wall" class="rounded-t-lg" /></figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Great Green Wall </h2>
          <p>An African Union initiative to restore degraded Sahel landscape(trees, food forest etc) to reduce deserrification, sequester carbon and create green jobs. </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="greenwall.ejs" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Third Project  -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
        <figure><img src="mangrove.avif" alt="Mangrove" class="rounded-t-lg" /></figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Mangrove - "Blue Carbon" restoration projects</h2>
          <p>Community-led mangrove planting and wetland restoration to lock carbon into coastal soils, protect coasts and support fisheries and livelihoods</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="mangrove.ejs" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
